* Note: {@link WifiConfiguration#SSID} & {@link WifiConfiguration#BSSID} fields from * WifiConfiguration are not used. Instead we use the {@link #ssidPatternMatcher} & * {@link #bssidPatternMatcher} fields embedded directly * within {@link WifiNetworkSpecifier}. * @hide
